data.description: Beautiful brick ranch, 4 bedroom, 1.5 bath home in Northwestern schools. 2000+ sq feet. Mature trees, beautiful secluded yard. Soak up that country feel, close to town and all its amenities. Large back patio. Grand family room fireplace. Gorgeous hardwood floors. Updated kitchen and appliances with luxury stone countertops. New control box, Water pressure tank, Septic tank emptied 2/23, New pump and float for septic system, New garbage disposal and Shed is 2 years young.  Garage was converted to 4th bedroom and can be converted back.
